channel.title: I need a bit of help with jdk6u3
channel.description:
hey, I'm having trouble getting onto testscape and every other source... yesterday i found my laptop decided to let me download things... so i downloaded jdk6u3, moparscape, and a few sources... but when i compile it says something about 'javac'.
on my old comp jdk6(no updates) had no probs at all. i got straight onto a server/source
if anyone has a little help for me, it would be much appreciated
